{"tid":750420,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好少輕度抑鬱症患者識食st john's wort","createTime":"2018-07-21T01:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T15:57:28.000Z","uid":113626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"21dacdf65c4749d6cd2d045e6b78ead421bad51b","tid":750420,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypericum_perforatum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHypericum_perforatum&d=%2Bo3dCIM5i4F2u9Sbvt8Am26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=efc8eaf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypericum_perforatum</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">It is a believed to be a medicinal herb with antidepressant activity, although high-quality clinical evidence for such effects is limited. </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/貫葉連翹\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%B2%AB%E8%91%89%E9%80%A3%E7%BF%B9&d=%2Bo3dCIM5i4F2u9Sbvt8Am26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6fdcb800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/貫葉連翹</a><br />\n<br />\n貫葉連翹（學名：Hypericum perforatum）， 又名貫葉金絲桃、聖約翰草（St John's wort），金絲桃科金絲桃屬植物，是歐美的常用草藥，主要用於婦女調經，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">有寧神、平衡情緒的作用，臨床上發現對抑鬱症患者有療效<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n係古代已經比人叫做開心草, d藥廠驚左d利潤所以d research一路都唔敢大型研究呢隻野實際功效, 但事實有少量外國paper已經講到明有幾乎同藥同等功能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保健品黎, 就咁買到...通街d藥房/萬寧都有 (連藥物範圍都納唔入, 當係保健品範圍)<br />\n重點係唔想比人label有睇精神科/驚食精神科藥其實可以買黎試下"},{"pid":"ec05b2e538faccf90971f8ad99fc30c216480173","tid":750420,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21dacdf65c4749d6cd2d045e6b78ead421bad51b","tid":750420,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypericum_perforatum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2F